{"tid":2204189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不許汉地有藏傳佛教  著名唐代藏式千年古寺整改後仍被拆毀","createTime":"2020-09-16T01:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:08:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"595b54b565ad38c63211f3de4d4b0f48ff1d5675","tid":2204189,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:12:22.000Z","msg":"福雲寺位於山西省晉中市榆次區烏金山鎮，始建於唐代（618年&mdash;907年），2002年至2011年耗資兩千餘萬元（人民幣，下同。約合290多萬美元）復修、擴建後，建築面積達二千餘平方米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/%E7%A6%8F%E4%BA%91%E5%AF%BA%E5%8E%9F%E8%B2%8C1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E7%25A6%258F%25E4%25BA%2591%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E5%258E%259F%25E8%25B2%258C1.jpg&h=56fb435b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福雲寺原貌<br />\n<br />\n福雲寺兼有藏傳佛教與漢傳佛教特徵，是政府批准的合法宗教場所。2017年，當地政府曾宣稱計劃引資3億元（約合4390萬美元）打造福雲寺、和合寺佛教旅遊區。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，政府的計劃改變，當年11月，當地佛教協會勒令拆除福雲寺內傳統的藏文經幡，移走兩個藏式銅佛像。<br />\n<br />\n今年7月21日，政府出動一輛鏟車、多輛挖掘機，將福雲寺藏式風格的房頂和牆壁上的鎏金標誌全部拆除，通往福雲寺的路被警察把守，禁止民眾去寺廟。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，住在寺廟裡的和尚被趕走，寺廟被關閉，政府人員對聞訊前來的民眾聲稱要整改寺廟。<br />\n<br />\n這是個騙局。兩天後，當局趁夜強拆福雲寺。當地一居民告訴《寒冬》，那天晚上9點，8輛挖掘機和1輛鏟車以及10多輛貨車陸續開到了福雲寺。<br />\n<br />\n一目擊者稱，警察、城管人員、村幹部搗毀幾尊佛像，掏走佛像肚子裡的值錢物品，並把紅木桌椅都拉走。<br />\n<br />\n次日凌晨5點，福雲寺被夷為平地。據當地一名政府人員透露，拆除福雲寺是正在進行的對漢人區藏傳佛教打擊行動的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/%E7%A6%8F%E4%BA%91%E5%AF%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%9C%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B7%E4%B8%BA%E5%B9%B3%E5%9C%B0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F%25E7%25A6%258F%25E4%25BA%2591%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%259C%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%2597%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A4%25B7%25E4%25B8%25BA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259C%25B0.jpg&h=45b29e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福雲寺一夜之間被夷為平地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/a-thousand-year-old-tibetan-buddhist-temple-destroyed-in-shanxi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fa-thousand-year-old-tibetan-buddhist-temple-destroyed-in-shanxi%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTve9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=c4ff196d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/a-thousand-year-old-tibetan-buddhist-temple-destroyed-in-shanxi/</a>"},{"pid":"31a92695174a1efb089011df3d4d5d782b5da1eb","tid":2204189,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b69dfe38115f969f727d00b30134f24d4ad9bd7f","tid":2204189,"uid":28068,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"夠膽滅佛<br />\n等睇亡國報應"},{"pid":"828edec27995c505002d21aa69839085d705bfcf","tid":2204189,"uid":109262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:19:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">支<br />\n那<br />\n人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7122b022cc4d18fc164148de1f08be43500cd846","tid":2204189,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n<br />\n五台山呢個佛教中心，有幾家喇嘛廟，唔知幾時拆？"},{"pid":"b154929be37bbdffbcf76cdbfc51053ec4a42961","tid":2204189,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:22:10.000Z","msg":"遲早兵馬俑都講到會顛覆國家政權<br />\n秦始皇條咸魚都要拎番出嚟鞭"},{"pid":"b9d6bf52b4a94480b7f258858ea35859d2497e29","tid":2204189,"uid":137159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"共武帝滅佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eeaa8758537732e3cf59fca60adfd4befb688f","tid":2204189,"uid":31796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"信唔信遲啲連西遊記去天竺取經都唔俾講<br />\n要改去北京取經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cla